00:28:22,367 --> 00:28:26,162
"The fact that we smiled
and talked under that tree

306
00:28:28,039 --> 00:28:29,165
will be long-forgotten."

307
00:28:32,085 --> 00:28:34,504
"But every year in spring,

308
00:28:36,423 --> 00:28:37,257
that tree…

309
00:28:48,476 --> 00:28:49,728
will remember our laughter,

310
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:53,648
our breath,

311
00:28:57,777 --> 00:28:58,820
and our voices…

312
00:29:01,322 --> 00:29:02,323
to leaf out,

313
00:29:06,244 --> 00:29:07,454
