315
00:29:15,044 --> 00:29:16,588
We Sat Face to Face.

316
00:29:17,172 --> 00:29:19,924
Gosh, it made my heart leap.

317
00:29:20,008 --> 00:29:20,842
Right.

318
00:29:20,925 --> 00:29:24,304
I feel something like that
in my heart too.

319
00:29:24,888 --> 00:29:27,056
-You do?
-Can't I?

320
00:29:27,140 --> 00:29:27,974
