321
00:29:30,852 --> 00:29:34,898
So Yeong-su,
can you tell us what brought you here?

322
00:29:34,981 --> 00:29:37,025
-Right.
-I heard he really likes books.

323
00:29:37,108 --> 00:29:40,236
He's the unicorn of our school.
