324
00:29:40,320 --> 00:29:42,739
You're here because you like books. Right?

325
00:29:42,822 --> 00:29:47,076
-A unicorn.
-Fun fact. Hwi has a big crush on him,

326
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:50,330
-but he has no interest in her.
-Excuse me.

327
00:29:50,413 --> 00:29:52,207
Can you please use the past tense?

328
00:29:52,290 --> 00:29:53,833
Because I'm over him now.

329
00:29:53,917 --> 00:29:54,834
Nice to meet you.

330
00:29:54,918 --> 00:29:58,046
I'm Lee Jang-u, the unicorn
of the 42nd class at Hyecheon High School.

331
00:29:58,129 --> 00:30:00,924
I see you're good-looking, just like me.

332
00:30:01,007 --> 00:30:02,217
Is that why she likes you?

333
00:30:02,300 --> 00:30:04,427
Hello? I just said to use the past tense.

334
00:30:04,511 --> 00:30:06,346
You don't seem to know what that means.

335
00:30:06,429 --> 00:30:10,725
Do you really think Hwi likes him
only because of his looks?

336
00:30:10,809 --> 00:30:11,810
Well,

337
00:30:11,893 --> 00:30:14,229
