where looks matter the most.

338
00:30:14,312 --> 00:30:17,607
Listen, everyone. It is all in the past.

339
00:30:17,690 --> 00:30:19,400
Don't you know what that word means?

340
00:30:19,484 --> 00:30:20,860
How is it in the past?

341
00:30:20,944 --> 00:30:22,153
But it is.

342
00:30:22,237 --> 00:30:24,322
Right, if that's what Hwi says--

343
00:30:24,405 --> 00:30:25,949
