377
00:31:44,277 --> 00:31:45,486
Is that okay?

378
00:31:45,570 --> 00:31:47,322
Sure, ask away.

379
00:31:47,405 --> 00:31:49,574
I'm all ears.

380
00:31:51,743 --> 00:31:54,537
So you're holding
a coffee festival in Gangneung.

381
00:31:54,621 --> 00:31:55,580
Recommend me baristas.

382
00:31:55,663 --> 00:31:58,625
And you'd like famous baristas…
Hey, this is why you called?

383
00:31:58,708 --> 00:32:01,419
Yes. Why? Am I not supposed to?

384
00:32:02,503 --> 00:32:03,463
If so, I can ask--

385
00:32:03,546 --> 00:32:06,883
No! There's no need.
I can help you with that.

386
00:32:07,592 --> 00:32:10,178
Jang-u, I knew I could count on you.
Thank you.

387
00:32:10,261 --> 00:32:12,096
I promise I will make it up to you.

388
00:32:12,180 --> 00:32:13,389
Wait.

389
00:32:13,473 --> 00:32:17,018
-Yes?
-Did you have anything else to say?

390
00:32:18,186 --> 00:32:19,103
No.

391
00:32:19,854 --> 00:32:22,774
I see. Okay. Enjoy your lunch.

392
00:32:22,857 --> 00:32:24,567
Lunch? It's four o'clock.

393
00:32:24,651 --> 00:32:26,194
You have a nice lunch yourself.

394
00:32:26,277 --> 00:32:29,322
Yes, I will. I will have lunch.

395
00:32:29,405 --> 00:32:31,074
Right, I will enjoy my lunch now.

396
00:32:32,325 --> 00:32:34,035
-Bye.
-Bye.

397
00:32:43,127 --> 00:32:46,172
Gosh, this is the first time
we've talked on the phone.

