make sense to you?

428
00:34:27,190 --> 00:34:28,816
-No, of course not.
-Right.

429
00:34:30,234 --> 00:34:31,819
Wait. Listen up.

430
00:34:31,903 --> 00:34:36,657
I think you've all fallen
for my unbelievable charm.

431
00:34:36,741 --> 00:34:37,825
Do you get it?

432
00:34:38,868 --> 00:34:42,121
-Goodness. They're totally into me.
